228
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:22,630
Eso es todo.

229
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:38,039
Conocerse

230
00:20:38,760 --> 00:20:41,593
en Hiroshima.

231
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,758
No pasa cada día.

232
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:49,109
