Io entiendes...

724
01:10:40,720 --> 01:10:41,675
Vete.

725
01:10:44,920 --> 01:10:46,876
Imposible dejarte.

726
01:11:11,120 --> 01:11:14,237
Quédate en Hiroshima conmigo.

727
01:11:21,720 --> 01:11:23,438
Vendrá hacia mi,

728
01:11:24,920 --> 01:11:27,036
